<emphasis id="61B6EAB4FFFBFFE5E05501EDFE10FE12" bold="true" box="[367,435,439,465]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="28">tatara</emphasis>
</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFFBFFE5E08301EDFD2BFE12" author="Krulikovsky, A." box="[441,648,439,465]" pageId="3" pageNumber="28" pagination="200 - 251" refId="ref9900" refString="Krulikovsky, A. (1891) Experimental catalogue of Lepidoptera of Kazakh Province. Bullitin de la Societe Imperiale des Naturalistes de Moscou (New Series) 4, 200 - 251. [In Russian, colour pls. I - VIII]" type="journal article" year="1891">Krulikovsky, 1891</bibRefCitation>
